            <h3>cup: {ing.cup}</h3>
            <h3>mL: {ing.ml}</h3>
            <h3>L: {ing.L}</h3>
            <h3>oz: {ing.oz}</h3>
            <h3>lb: {ing.lb}</h3>
            <h3>g: {ing.g}</h3>
            </p>
            </CardContent>
            </Card>
        ))
            
